{
  "texts": [
    "It is important to note that while our rating was based on the AHRQ scale, it should be considered as a subjective assessment.",
    "The evaluation of satisfaction is crucial because relying solely on technical metrics, such as accuracy, may not fully capture users' genuine needs and expectations.",
    "Also, the satisfaction assessment offered three options: Satisfied, Fair, and Unsatisfied.",
    "The inter-rater agreement was also calculated using Fleiss' kappa, which is the same metric used in the evaluation of the generated reports.",
    "npj Digital Medicine | (2024) 7:111"
  ]
}